<h2>Raspberry pi 3 B</h2>

<p>Price ~30 eur</p>

<p>The heart of Tarina. Why Raspberry pi you ask? There are several reasons:</p>

<ul>
<li>Available everywhere.</li>
<li>Huge support.</li>
<li>The great Debian based os Raspbian (beeing a debian nerd myself).</li>
<li>Low price.</li>
<li>Picamera.</li>
</ul>

<p>The 3B+ is too powerhungry for the Powerbooster 1000C thats why I went with 3B</p>

