<h1>Post processing</h1>

<p>This is still a work in progress...</p>

<p>So far I've come to this conclusion:</p>

<ul>
<li>Sanded with multiple grit/sandpaper from rough to the finest (from 120 to 400)</li>
<li>Paint first two layers</li>
<li>Sand again</li>
<li>Paint two layers again</li>
<li>Continue til satisfied</li>
</ul>

